    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've seen some biohacking forums saying that mega-dosing for a short burst is actually how you \"reset\" your levels when you're super deficient. wouldn't the body just process the excess if it's only for like 10 or 14 days? it seems like a lot of unnecessary hassle to go to a doctor just for a quick boost.",
