      "content": "Those biohacking forums are filled with anecdotal, unverified claims, and relying on them for serious supplementation is risky. Your body has limits, and sudden, massive doses can overwhelm your system, leading to hypercalcemia, which is a serious medical issue. Instead of guesswork, a quick consultation to get a baseline blood level is the only way to ensure your \"reset\" is safe and effective.",
      "source": "target",
